<h1 style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #111827;">Your Delivery is Tomorrow!</h1>
<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
  Hey <%= @user.name %>, your car is on its way! Here's a quick reminder:
</p>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color: #e0f7fc; border: 1px solid #b2ebf2; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 4px; font-size: 12px; color: #0090b3; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Delivery Time</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 20px; color: #111827; font-weight: 800;"><%= @appointment.scheduled_date.strftime('%A, %B %d') %> at <%= @appointment.scheduled_time.strftime('%I:%M %p') %></p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">Quick checklist:</h3>
<ul style="margin: 0 0 24px; padding-left: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
  <li>Have your driver's license ready</li>
  <li>Ensure your insurance is active</li>
  <li>Clear a parking spot for your new car</li>
  <li>We'll call you 30 minutes before arrival</li>
</ul>
